###
## hipgpg :: send encrpyted messages to hipchat
## rev 20120206 c3w@juicypop.net
## obtain hipchat-cli from https://github.com/hipchat/hipchat-cli/blob/master/hipchat_room_message

REQUIREMENTS
	gpg, hipchat-cli, bash


INSTALLATION
Customize hipchatrc-dist and copy to ~/.hipchatrc
Ensure you have everybody's keys to encrypt to

RUNTIME
hipgpg someuser@wherever.com hey man the passwd is g0rk!

VERIFY
Your encrypted message will appear in the hipchat channel specified in ~/.hipchatrc, with the recipient email in plain text
